data.description: "Uncover the hidden gem at 1538 Stoneleigh Hill Rd, Lithonia, GA 30058! This 5-bed, 4-bath fixer-upper boasts incredible potential, offering the canvas for your dream home. Nestled on a spacious lot, the property features a serene backyard oasis with a picturesque lake, providing a tranquil retreat. Imagine the possibilities and make this residence your own, crafting a masterpiece in a prime location. Seize the opportunity to transform this house into your vision of home sweet home!"
